Chhit
“Lan2 si7 m7-si7 ai3 chiam7-si5 li7-khui Puigcerda Nuevo? Na7 soann-kha e5 hiong-chhin hou7 lan2 e5 im-sin3, cheng3-hu2 i2-keng khai-si2 teh chhiok-na2 pau-khoah ‘Ka-nng5 i-ti7’, ‘Lau2-sit8 seng-li2-lang5’, ‘Lau2-sit8 kong-bu7-oan5’ teng2-teng2 e5 iu2-chi3, koh lai5 beh ka7 Puigcerda Nuevo biat8-bo5 e5 siau-sit ma7 thoan5 kah hong-siann pong7-iann2, si7 m7-si7 sio2 phiah-chau2--chit8-e5 khah ho2?” Chit8-e5 khoann3--khi2-lai5 lak8-chap8 goa7 hoe3 e5 lau2-toa7-lang5 an2-ne kong2.
A-tek loh8-soann e5 te7-it-kang, chng-thau5 lai7-te2 to7 khui-hoe7 teh tho2-lun7 chit-khui3 e5 se3-bin7.
“Lan2 si7 an2-choann2 ai3 lai5-chau2? Lan2 tau3-te2 si7 to2-ui7 cho3 m7-tioh8, tann si7 an2-choann2 be7-su thau-chiah8-kau2 u7-choe7?” chit8-e5 gou7-chap8 thong2 hoe3 e5 cha-pou-lang5 teh kong2-oe7, “A-peh, phainn2-se3, an2-ne ka7 li2 keh8-oe7, m7-koh siunn7 tong-hoan-chhou chit-e5 sou2-chai7 khi2-ki e5 li2-siong2, beh ka7 jin5-lui7 e5 bi7-lai5 kai2-i5, beh thau3-te2 kai2-koat jin5-lui7 e5 bun7-te5, chit kui2-a7 chap8 tang, lan2 bo5 eng7 chheng3, bo5 eng7 to, lan2 mi5-noa7 chhiann5-chhi5 lan2 e5 chu2-te7 chhut-thau chhut-kioh, ti7 tak8-tou5 long2 tah8 tioh8 ho2 te7-pou7, chit-ma2 lan2 e5 lang5 chhoa7-thau5--ah, lan2 e5 kang-su7 chiah tu2 khi2-khian3, lan2 e5 chhiu2-lou7 long2 kong-beng5 cheng3-tai7, chit-e5 si5-tai7, goa2 m7-sin3 cheng3-hu2 e7 eng7 kiong5-hoat, sai2 kek8-pou7.”
Chit-e5 cha-pou-lang5 teh kong2-oe7 e5 si5, u7 chit8-koa2 che7 ti7 pinn--a2 e5 lang5 teh tim3-thau5 piau2-si7 tong5-i3, ma7 u7-lang5 chhi-bu2-chhi-chhu7 m7-chai teh kong2 siann2.
“He chhiu2 si7 senn ti7 lang5 e5 sin-khu teng2, na7 lang5 beh an2-choann2 siunn7 ma7-si7 chai7-lang5--e5, chit-toann7 si5-kan e7 lai5 hoat-seng sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3, u7-iann2 chin oh pan7-phoe, goa2 jin7-ui7 lan2 tai7-ke long2 ai3 ui7 tioh8 ka-ti7 kap chhu3--nih8 e5 lang5 phah-sng3, na7 u7 an3-sng3 beh seng li7-khui chit8-cham7-a2--e5, lan2 to7 m7-thang bak8-chiu phah sann-kak.” Lau2-lang5 koh kong2.
Chit-chun7 e5 chap8-it goeh8-thinn m7-na7 hou7 lang5 kam2-kak chhiu-chhin3, pun2-te2 ti7 jit8-thau5 chhut--lai5 chin3-cheng5, soann-lai7 to7 long2 khah leng2, in-ui7 chit-cham7-a2 e5 tai7-chi3, tai7-ke e5 sim-cheng5 long2 toe3 thinn-khi3 e5 pian3-hoa3 teh au3-loh8, lian5 thinn-teng2 goan5-te2 eng3-kai si7 khin-io5-io5 e5 hun5, khoann3-tioh8 long2 an5-tu-tu, kan2-na2 ma7 sam3-tam7 sam3-tam7, liam-pinn e7 siak to3--loh8-lai5.
Am3-thau5-a2 lak8-tiam2 goa7, jit8-thau5 iau2 bo5 i3-su3 beh loh8-khi3 hioh-khun3, Saint Fulgentius penn7-inn7 chhin-chhiunn7 chit8-e5 ou-sek toa7-thah chhai7 ti7 toa7-ke e5 lou7-pinn, chit-si3-khou-ui5 m7-si7 siann5-chhi7 lai7-te2 khah lau7-jiat8 e5 sou2-chai7, lou7--nih8 chhia kap lang5 long2 chiann5 chio2, A-tek tiam7-tiam7 tui3 mng5-chhui3 kiann5--jip8-khi3, na2 kiann5 na2 teh siunn7 beh an2-choann2 chiah chhoe7 e7 tioh8 Ngou5 Kok-seng5.
I khi3-kau3 kui7-tai5 mng7 u7 chit8-e5 toa3-inn7 e5 lang5 ho7-cho3 Silvio Ngo5 bo5, long2 mng7 bo5, A-tek m7 si2-sim, koh mng7 “NNgou5 Kok-seng5” chit-e5 Han3-mai5, kang7-khoan2 mng7 bo5, chit-e5 lau2-lang5 kap kui-kiann7 tai7-chi3 khak-sit8 u7-kau3 sin5-pi3.
I che7 tian7-thui chiunn7-lau5, na2 teh khoann3 kao3 ti7 piah-teng2 e5 “lau5-chan3 soeh-beng5”, bo5-tiunn-ti5 khi3 chu3-i3 tioh8 kau2-lau5 si7 i-su e5 pan7-kong-sek, i sui5 ka7 kau2-lau5 e5 an3-niu2 chhih8--loeh.
Chit-e5 chhut tian7-thui-mgn5, to7 khoann3-tioh8 chit8-tiunn ko3-si7, kong2 chia si7 pan7-kong tiunn5-sou2, chhiann2 lang5-kheh theng5-kha, A-tek seng khia7--leh, khoann3 cheng5 khoann3 au7, khak-sit8 bo5-lang5, chiah kin2 kiann5--chhut-khi3.
I tui3 hang7-lou7 tit8-tit8 kiann5--loeh, hang7-lou7 chit8-peng5 si7 ng3 tui3 goa7-khau2 kui-pai5 e5 po-le5 thang-a2, leng7-goa7 chit8-peng5 si7 chit8-keng chit8-keng e5 pan7-kong-sek, mng5-pan2 e5 teng2-bin7 long2 u7 koa3 mia5-pai5.
A-tek kiann5 lai5-kau3 oat-kak e5 sou2-chai7, chu3-i3 tioh8 chit8-keng pan7-kong-sek mng5-teng2 e5 mia5-pai5 sia2--e5 si7 “Juan Lorca”, i kin2 oa2--koe3, tui3 mng5-piann2 chun7 khoann3-mai7, mng5 so2-tiau5--leh.
I hiong5-hiong5 siunn7 tioh8 ti7 ki-kim-hoe7 Juan e5 tong5-su7 hou7 i e5 so2-si5, kin2 tui3 khou3-te7-a2 jim5--chhut-lai5, tui3 so2-si5-khang chhah--jip8-khi3, koh u7 hoan2-eng3, chun7--chit8-e5, mng5 “phiak8”--chit8-e5 khui--khui.
Mng5 sak--khui e5 si5-chun7, hoat-chhut “koainn5” chit8-siann, A-tek khi3 hou7 chhoah chit8-tio5, kin2 bih jip8-khi3 pang5-keng lai7-te2, ka7 mng5 koainn--khi2-lai5.
“Juan hit-e5 tong5-su7 ma7 iang goa2 lai5 kiu3 Ngou5 Kok-seng5, koh hou7 goa2 Juan pan7-kong-sek e5 so2-si5, chit-keng pan7-kong-sek lai7-te2 tiann7-tioh8 u7 siann2 soann3-soh, e7-tang3 hou7 goa2 chhoe7 tioh8 NNgou5 phok-su7.”
I si3-koe3 na2 peng2 na2 khoann3, khoann3 e7 chhut--lai5, Juan e7 lau5 chiah che7 mih8-kiann7 ti7 chia, kiam2-chhai2 si7 phai3-phoe i e7 koh tng2--lai5, sou2-i2 bo5 ka7 mih8-kiann7 long2 ka7 khoan2-chau2.
I bo5-i3-tiong khoann3-tioh8 oa2 ti7 piah-pinn e5 thih-tu5 teng2, u7 he7 chin che7 file, ki5-tiong u7 chit8-e5 file kap ki5-thann e5 file long2 bo5-kang5, ki5-thann e5 file si7 sim2-mih8 chu-liau7 long2 phaiu kah chiann5 beng5, to7 chun2-kong2 si7 A-tek m7-bat e5 i-hak8 mia5-su5, siong7-bo5 be7 chhin-chhiunn7 chit-pun2 sia2 kah chiah-nih8 kan2-tan, teng2-thau5 tah-choa2 kan-tann sia2 “SKSN” si3-e5 ji7-bu2.
A-tek ka7 hit-e5 file theh8--loh8-lai5, hian--khui, file lai7-te2 u7 chit8-thah si7 ui3 sin-bun5-choa2 ka--loh8-lai5, cheng2-li2 kah ho2-se3 ho2-se3 e5 chu-liau7, hiah-e5 sin-bun5 long2 i2-keng chin ku2--ah, choa2 i2-keng sio2-khoa2 chhe3-chhe3 ng5-ng5, i hoat-hian7 chiah-e5 sin-bun5 e5 chu2-te5 long2 kap chit8-e5 lang5 u7 koan-he7, u7-e5 sou2-chai7 kio3 i “Silvio Ngo5”, u7-e5 sou2-chai7 ka7 kio3-cho3 “Ngo5 Kok-seng5”. A-tek chit-chun7 chiah chai-khang, “SKSN” to7-si7 “Silvio Kok-seng5 Ngo5” e5 kan2-sia2.
Hiah-e5 sin-bun5 e5 au7-piah si7 chit8-koa2 penn7-lek8 kap ki3-lok8, A-tek ti7 teng2-thau5 khoann3-tioh8 chit8-e5 pang5-keng ho7-be2 1200.
I ka7 chit-e5 file theh8--leh, sun7-soa3 hiann3 chit8-nia2 Juan lau5--loh8-lai5, tiau3-ti7 piah-teng2 e5 peh8-sek tng5-sann, thah8 ti7 sin-khu-teng2, i kiann5-chhut pan7-kong-sek, chau2-lai5 chhih8 tian7-thui, bo5-liong7 kong2 be7 chin7 chhih8 tioh8, tian7-thui-mng5 soah khui--khui, A-tek in-ui7 sim-hi bo5 ke-siunn7 siann2, hoan-thau5 to7 long7, i thiann-tioh8 tian7-thui lai7-te2 u7 chit8-e5 cha-pou kap chit8-e5 cha-bou2 kiann5 to2 chhut--lai5, koh na2 kiann5 na2 teh kong2-oe7, i m7-kann2 oat8-thau5 khoann3, kan-tann tit8-tit8 the5-chhinn2 ka-ti7 ai3 tek-tiann7, ka7 kha-pou7 ban7--loh8-lai5, hoan7-se3 si7 in-ui7 i thah8 chit8-nia2 i-su e5 peh8-sek tng5-sann, sou2-i2 bo5 hou7 lang5 khi2-gi5.
I koat-teng7 beh kiann5 lau5-thui khi2-lih chap8-ji7 lau5,   toe3 ho7-thau5 kiann5 tng2-lai5 oat-kak e5 sou2-chai7, to2-oat, khoann3-tioh8 lau5-thui-keng e5 mng5 to7 ti7 chiann3-peng5,  A-tek chim-chiok thiann, khak-teng7 tu2-chiah hit nng7-e5 lang5 bo5 toe3--koe3-lai5, i chiah loh8-sim.
I sak-mng5, sann-pou7 cho3 chit8-hoah8 kiann5 jip8-khi3 lau5-thui-keng.
(Tai5-bun5 Bong2-po3 te7 100~102 ki5, 2005 ni5 1~3 goeh8)
